    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/2e9ebfc895ffe4b2806ba164395d5e41.poster.avif?t=1768902819\" width=480 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/2e9ebfc895ffe4b2806ba164395d5e41.webm?t=1768902819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The I.S.A recorded mysterious changes in Venus's climate. After failing to colonize Mars, it may be humanity’s best hope of escaping Earth. However, all probes have vanished, and now you volunteered for a solo mission to explore the planet’s dark secrets. For mankind, it’s Venus or die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >VENUS OR DIE is a short atmospheric horror game from the multi-award-winning Blue Desert Studios.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/46ac78bac8c2d131d1952090e51c80bd.poster.avif?t=1768902819\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/46ac78bac8c2d131d1952090e51c80bd.webm?t=1768902819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/46ac78bac8c2d131d1952090e51c80bd.mp4?t=1768902819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Navigate the shadows of Venus in a six-wheeled exploration vehicle on a solo mission to investigate why the planet's climate is changing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/3969c44a3f4c3a9f8012b4de2ca15c68.poster.avif?t=1768902819\" width=480 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/3969c44a3f4c3a9f8012b4de2ca15c68.webm?t=1768902819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore and collect samples to unpack the mystery and avoid the pitfalls of the planet's dark secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/d0f2a4f4b535ddbd5c0e00fcb4dd3855.poster.avif?t=1768902819\" width=480 height=128 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/d0f2a4f4b535ddbd5c0e00fcb4dd3855.webm?t=1768902819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Venus featuring actual satellite terrain data.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Vehicular platforming and exploration of a lonely and unforgiving planet </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play in an atmospheric and claustrophobic environment</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beautiful AA Visuals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short 1 - 2 Hour horror experience</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/956295ad5c836bfe8121e3746cdc1bb1.poster.avif?t=1768902819\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/956295ad5c836bfe8121e3746cdc1bb1.webm?t=1768902819\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273040/extras/956295ad5c836bfe8121e3746cdc1bb1.mp4?t=1768902819\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
